text: Caeli McKay (born 25 June 1999) is a Canadian diver. She competed in the women's 10 metre platform event at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female divers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in diving Category:Commonwealth Games silver medallists for Canada Category:Divers at the 2018 Commonwealth Games Category:Pan American Games medalists in diving Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Canada Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Canada Category:Divers at the 2019 Pan American Games
